  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Ovarian reserve influenced by many factor but especially cysts like endometrioma. Anti
      mullerian hormone is recent marker for ovarian reserve. The investigators are searching
      ovarian reserve pre and post operatively by using antimullerian hormone of endometrioma
      patient who are operated for their cysts.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
